{"tid":1647953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【果燃台1pm LIVE】網民再發「黨鐵商場和你Shop 2.0」 齋睇唔買杯葛港鐵","createTime":"2019-10-12T03:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:21:03.000Z","uid":61886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"395aaabf85f4d7a115ca6c41de5428fc82c79401","tid":1647953,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:36:18.000Z","msg":"【果燃台1pm LIVE】網民再發「黨鐵商場和你Shop 2.0」 齋睇唔買杯葛港鐵<br />\n<br />\n繼上星期十八區各大商場「和你Shop 2.0」，網民再發起「黨鐵商場和你Shop 2.0」，計劃今午到港鐵旗下的商埸Window Shopping，及進行全商場「裝飾」，發起人強調活動是合家歡的活動，目標是要令商場暫停營業。《蘋果》屆時將進行直播。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191012/60145257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60145257&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=7a0e2a8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60145257&h=547801bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191012/60145257</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z34VEUV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ34VEUV.jpg&h=4e0a0cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道三點有尖沙咀大遊行<br />\n希望唔好分散人數<br />\n<br />\n所以有以下建議<br />\n<br />\n1. 如果帶住小朋友嘅<br />\n覺得遊行太危險<br />\n可以考慮去和理Shop<br />\n<br />\n2. 遊行前可以早啲出到黎嘅<br />\n先去商場熱身<br />\n<br />\n3. 遊行途中出橙旗或黑旗<br />\n如果有和理非覺得危險離開既<br />\n可選擇轉去黨鐵商場和你Shop<br />\n<br />\n4. 遊行完嘅都可以去嘆下冷氣<br />\n<br />\n一陣見"},{"pid":"9be2224c97ac3f5444c4071f20064d0e26f7a0e9","tid":1647953,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:37:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67c5a963c5ba796417d08d0a1da2d748fed9d403","tid":1647953,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:39:24.000Z","msg":"真係去既<br />\n大家帶啲文宣幫藍店裝飾下"},{"pid":"a1440d1d3e0bbf1d8581221d3f6d44e73a0010e7","tid":1647953,"uid":296112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:57:52.000Z","msg":"希望成事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa1b458f3cb5cc64ad7226be033dda599c5708a","tid":1647953,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e11e29c323d8cd45d8490b61ae6b83bb03f8a668","tid":1647953,"uid":198214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:21:03.000Z","msg":"幫推"}]}